        Yes, we strive to provide organic and locally sourced products whenever possible. We believe in supporting local farmers and promoting sustainable agriculture.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="ticketdiv">
    <p>
        <strong><span>How can I place an order?</span></strong><br />
        You can place an order through our website. Simply browse our product catalog, select the items you want, and proceed to checkout.
    </p>
